{"tid":1435170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【修例風波】17發展商聯署 地建會譴責暴力行為違和平示威原意","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:05:10.000Z","uid":188430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f87b70a35b44cb64ea73cb3f0046cacb827f7d72","tid":1435170,"uid":188430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GRZ5DY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRZ5DY3.jpg&h=d58f3a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港因《逃犯條例》修訂問題引發的社會衝突愈演愈激烈之際，香港地產建設商會今日發表聲明，指近日社會因為一少部分暴力人士的行為而蒙上陰影，不但已偏離眾多和平示威者的原意，工商團體至市民大眾亦深受困擾。<br />\n<br />\n香港地產建設商會表示，對日益升級的暴力作出強烈譴責，希望香港儘早回歸安寧與法治，人人安居樂業。<br />\n<br />\n至於聯署的地產商會員，包括華懋、長實（1113）、恒隆地產（0101）、恒地（0012）、 香港置地、合和（0054）、和記地產、希慎（0014）、嘉華（0173）、鷹君（0041）、麗展（0488）、新世界（0017）、信德（0242）、信置（0083）、新地（0016）、太古地產（1972）、會德豐（0020）。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1565253313394&amp;issue=20190808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1565253313394%26issue%3D20190808&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b5f48262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1565253313394&amp;issue=20190808</a>"},{"pid":"1845e6dac163000e467ed9f11ae6d7a8b53b6c55","tid":1435170,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"：我啲樓價俾你班廢青推冧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}